    "en": {
      "title": "A financial support of 200 million dollars from the Asian Development Bank",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Foreign media reported that the Asian Development Bank has approved an emergency financial assistance of 200 million dollars to Sri Lanka.",
        "The foreign media pointed out that this financial support has been provided by rescheduling the funds of the projects approved by the Asian Development Bank for Sri Lanka.",
        "The Asian Development Bank said the loan will be used to protect the livelihoods of vulnerable and poor families and increase food security."
      ],
